I once told K that he is an idiot.

01:39:26.625 --> 01:39:29.375
Love shouldn't be that complicated.

01:39:31.166 --> 01:39:33.291
He should've just told Cream
how he really felt.

01:39:37.583 --> 01:39:39.041
But it turns out I was the idiot.

01:39:41.208 --> 01:39:43.166
I didn't understand the meaning of love.

01:39:44.875 --> 01:39:46.708
Love needs sacrifice.

01:39:49.583 --> 01:39:51.083
The truth is,

01:39:51.166 --> 01:39:53.541
the biggest happiness for K is

01:39:54.708 --> 01:39:56.416
to see Cream happy.

01:39:58.916 --> 01:40:00.125
And Cream

01:40:02.125 --> 01:40:06.041
was willing to do anything
to make him happy

01:40:07.500 --> 01:40:10.500
and peaceful before he died.

01:40:16.250 --> 01:40:19.208
How would an idiot like me
understand this kind of love?

01:40:33.958 --> 01:40:38.541
Then I will be fine

01:40:38.625 --> 01:40:42.875
I just wish that this hurt

01:40:42.958 --> 01:40:46.625
Will subside

01:40:57.375 --> 01:40:58.625
Forever.

