When I was

01:41:19.708 --> 01:41:24.208
Fine

01:41:41.083 --> 01:41:43.708
Now, these lyrics fit.

01:41:45.208 --> 01:41:46.666
You try and sing it.

01:41:46.750 --> 01:41:48.333
Why me?

01:41:48.416 --> 01:41:49.666
Yeah, you.

01:41:49.750 --> 01:41:51.041
But I'm not a good singer.

01:41:51.125 --> 01:41:53.333
It's okay. It's just a demo.

01:41:54.416 --> 01:41:56.208
This is our song now.

01:41:56.291 --> 01:41:58.333
Later, people will remember us
every time they hear it.

01:41:58.916 --> 01:42:00.250
One day,

01:42:00.333 --> 01:42:02.958
someone will hear our song

01:42:03.041 --> 01:42:07.750
and remember that there was
someone named K and Cream.

01:42:10.291 --> 01:42:11.291
I'll record now.

01:42:12.625 --> 01:42:14.041
One, two…

01:42:19.875 --> 01:42:25.000
This song is for you

