You said that the world is

01:42:38.750 --> 01:42:41.458
Fine

01:42:42.875 --> 01:42:43.958
Yeah.

01:42:45.791 --> 01:42:49.250
Then I will be fine too

01:42:50.125 --> 01:42:53.708
I just wish that this hurt

01:42:53.791 --> 01:42:56.833
Will subside

01:42:57.625 --> 01:43:01.500
As I slowly forget

01:43:01.583 --> 01:43:06.416
Your voice

